* win: fix compilation against Windows 24H2 SDK (Thad House)

* win: remap ERROR_NOACCESS and ERROR_BUFFER_OVERFLOW (Jameson Nash)

* win,fs: match trailing slash presence in junctions to user input (Jameson
  Nash)


